    "Id": "610318",
    "ThreadId": "257083",
    "Html": "\r\n<p>I need to load my modules from the remote location in the same domain. The module URL is, for example,\r\n<a href=\"http://mysite/modules/modulea.xap\">http://mysite/modules/modulea.xap</a>.</p>\r\n<p>How do I configure ModuleInfo element in ModuleCatalog in order to achieve that?</p>\r\n<p>Thanks.</p>\r\n",
    "PostedDate": "2011-05-10T09:33:30.64-07:00",
    "UserRole": null,
    "MarkedAsAnswerDate": null
  },
  {
    "Id": "610362",
    "ThreadId": "257083",
    "Html": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 10pt;\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Hi,</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 10pt;\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">According to the <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">ModuleInfo</strong>&acute;s <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Ref</strong>&acute;s property summary in <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">ModuleInfo</strong> class:</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 10pt;\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&ldquo;<em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\">Reference to the location of the module assembly. The following are examples of valid <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">ModuleInfo.Ref</strong> values:</em></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&middot;</span></em><span style=\"font: 7pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><em><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">http://myDomain/ClientBin/MyModules.xap for remote module in Silverlight</span></span></span></strong></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 10pt 0.5in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><em><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-language: ES-AR; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&middot;</span><span style=\"line-height: normal; font-variant: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 7pt; font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></em><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><em>file://c:/MyProject/Modules/MyModule.dll for a loose DLL in WPF</em>.&rdquo;</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 10pt;\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">This means, in your <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">ModuleCatalog.xaml</strong> file, you could try setting the Ref property like this:</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">\r\n<div style=\"color: black; background-color: white;\">\r\n<pre><span style=\"color: blue;\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #a31515;\">Modularity</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">:</span><span style=\"color: #a31515;\">ModuleInfo</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">Ref</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">=</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">http://mysite/modules/modulea.xap</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">ModuleName</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">=</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ModuleA</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span> <br />     <span style=\"color: red;\">ModuleType</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">=</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"> ModuleA. ModuleA, ModuleA, Version=1.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=null</span><span style=\"color: black;\">\"</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">/&gt;</span>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 10pt;\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 10pt;\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">I hope you find this information useful.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 10pt;\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Thanks,</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 10pt;\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Miguel Bronzovic<br /><a href=\"http://blogs.southworks.net/mbronzovic\">http://blogs.southworks.net/mbronzovic</a></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 10pt;\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-language: ES-AR;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
